# Recipe Kitchen - Nutritionist agent

NAME nutritionist

INPUT task

GOAL analyze """
Analyze the recipe for nutritional content per serving:
- Macros: calories, protein, carbs, fat, fiber
- Key micronutrients: sodium, iron, calcium, vitamins
- Dietary flags: gluten-free, dairy-free, vegan, keto-friendly
- Health notes: allergens, high-sodium warnings
Suggest modifications for common dietary restrictions.
""" -> nutrition_report

RUN main USING analyze
